{"tid":1441862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與其擺垃圾fake news上黎問點拆，大家不如直接反攻","createTime":"2019-08-10T18:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:46:28.000Z","uid":55973,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f55fe9182b35c87b2c6948bced166d200145a372","tid":1441862,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:21:39.000Z","msg":"我發現依排多左好多唔知真心膠定三毛既人好鐘意不停貼對家既fake news出黎，跟住係度問點拆/點算好<br />\n<br />\n一黎依類post會令其他真係有用既資訊post沉底，二黎就算哂時間俾你搵到佢係fake news/改圖/吹水，對家都只會哦一聲，或者直接無視然後繼續貼其他流料<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地根本就無任何羞恥, 內疚之心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以與其成日擺垃圾fake news上黎問點拆，大家不如扮返佢地，係藍絲group將我地手頭上既大量核彈貼出黎，然後問返佢地點拆好<br />\n【唔該做返主動】我地渣住幾多核彈係手<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435712</a><br />\n例如貼721元朗鏗鏘集，然後用返佢地既語氣問係咪真，點拆好 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日開始再見到邊個擺藍絲fake news出黎我會當佢係鬼"},{"pid":"b652f073e20340bf9351d3064a75a4f34fa0da92","tid":1441862,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:22:11.000Z","msg":"811。約定你 「深水埗」「港島東」遊行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441682</a>"},{"pid":"76ec0084a43c23ce3feae3364a026a4a54a12956","tid":1441862,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:22:24.000Z","msg":"十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35080824082c8a31767c4ed72b03820c791140d6","tid":1441862,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09af1ded67578ad56372065384b4ce2764d03095","tid":1441862,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:22:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5568f383f31293f5a6